h3.
  Your Detector Feature Profile
p.
  The following feature profile was primarily created using <a href="http://www.modernizr.com/docs/#s2">Modernizr's core tests</a>. The left column of results, <strong>Your Browser</strong>, is populated by JavaScript using a copy of Modernizr that is loaded with this page. The right column, <strong>Detector Profile</strong>, is populated by PHP using the profile created by Detector for your browser.
  In addition to the core tests
  I've added an extended test that checks for emoji support as well as a per request test to check the device pixel ratio. Both were added using the <a href="http://www.modernizr.com/docs/#addtest">Modernizr.addTest() Plugin API</a>.
  To learn more about core, extended, and per request tests please <a href="https://github.com/dmolsen/Detector">review the README</a>.  To access any of these options in your PHP app you'd simply type <code>$ua->featureName</code>.

div.row
  div.text-center.clearfix Feature Profile Properties
  div.clearfix
    div.col-xs-6.col-sm-4.col-md-2.col-lg-2.col-xl-2.text-right.
      coreVersion:
    div.col-xs-6.ol-sm-8.col-md-10.col-lg-10.col-xl-10.
      This profile hasn't been versioned yet.
  div.clearfix
    div.col-xs-6.col-sm-4.col-md-2.col-lg-2.col-xl-2.text-right.
      family:
    div.col-xs-6.ol-sm-8.col-md-10.col-lg-10.col-xl-10.
      Feature family hasn't been set yet for this profile.

div.row
  each featureGroup in capabilities.sections
    div.group
      div.text-center.clearfix= featureGroup.title
      each feature in featureGroup.features
        div.clearfix
          if feature.specurl
            div.col-xs-6.col-sm-4.col-md-2.col-lg-2.col-xl-2.text-right
              a.title.spec(href=specurl title="Check the spec")= feature.title
          else
            div.title.col-xs-6.col-sm-4.col-md-2.col-lg-2.col-xl-2.text-right= feature.title

        div.col-xs-6.ol-sm-8.col-md-10.col-lg-10.col-xl-10(data-capability= feature.name)

        if feature.subfeatures
          each subfeature in feature.subfeatures
            div.clearfix
              div.title.col-xs-6.col-sm-4.col-md-2.col-lg-2.col-xl-2.text-right= subfeature.title
              div.col-xs-6.ol-sm-8.col-md-10.col-lg-10.col-xl-10(data-capability= subfeature.name)
